{"tid":567411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（依家d官咩料）商經局常秘　料年中處理植入式廣告規管修訂","createTime":"2018-02-20T22:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T10:05:18.000Z","uid":134683,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa8380bb16110828407a837c5af7c73e4b5dadc","tid":567411,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T22:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/062142_8eb79578c7a9698cef85e0005c6a806a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F062142_8eb79578c7a9698cef85e0005c6a806a.png&h=596b5bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府擬放寬傳統媒體跨媒體擁有權限制，今日起展開為期3個月的第一階段公眾諮詢。在今日相關記者會問答環節，有記者關注植入式廣告規管。商務及經濟發展局常任秘書長（通訊及創意產業）利敏貞表示，通訊事務管理局去年9月公布公眾對植入式廣告規管意見，調查發現有空間放寬當中規管。通訊局下一小組委員會，亦已於今年年初諮詢業界意見，稍後將推出新一輪公眾諮詢，料今年年中可以處理植入式廣告規管的修訂。"},{"pid":"e29e6dc73e9d1ee41ed48a4ddb4d4348b9af392e","tid":567411,"uid":85957,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T22:28:58.000Z","msg":"好得人驚，好似平時去圖書館見到嗰啲易服癖痴線佬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16327857b30d4c71b389de7dc1706574502f3b81","tid":567411,"uid":16956,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T22:42:50.000Z","msg":"壽衣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定新年衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de0010e37808391d65a03ccd57743098a75ad39","tid":567411,"uid":77196,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T22:45:42.000Z","msg":"分唔到男人定女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7319f59af7e3b92e527a8bc2338ee72bb44226c6","tid":567